{"tid":120883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港既人類發展指數(HDI)其實仲高過日本同北歐國家","createTime":"2017-02-14T18:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T10:11:30.000Z","uid":1567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99c215593cbbe4010efe4ee870d0f5db2afb3479","tid":120883,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港 0.910<br />\n瑞典 0.907<br />\n英國 0.907<br />\n韓國 0.898<br />\n日本 0.891<br />\n法國 0.888<br />\n芬蘭 0.883<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_Human_Development_Index\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_countries_by_Human_Development_Index&d=LMVY6Z7nIekaHefcscWgVZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=acdd5263\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_Human_Development_Index</a>"},{"pid":"b5085c48876fc934a76e46dbdc960bfe7dbbb025","tid":120883,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"思想保守<br />\n短視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ce638427253ec109ceeab6d9ff2c4c43eaf3d8","tid":120883,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:50:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce3b7da942a252f5f8aba6d9479e1d5e12bbade8","tid":120883,"uid":38242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:52:51.000Z","msg":"北歐唔多瞭解唔講，但日本確實唔會比香港優勝。無論係基建、經濟發展程度、平均收入、社會流通，統統都唔會比香港好。更何況日本社會階級分明森嚴，性別定型思想根深蒂固，仲有種種傳統規矩制度限制，作為日本人，生活嘅壓力比做香港人大得多。"},{"pid":"947eaeb2ace8abdb8152376ed86db1effbc7b307","tid":120883,"uid":1567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本係亞洲第一 點會低過香港</blockquote><br />\n亞洲第一係新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cee4541b9e4c2bde4bee05e79e4d1a0eaa9dbd9","tid":120883,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be3da9f6eab54e14aa24b6a4d99b780379bf1016","tid":120883,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:57:24.000Z","msg":"The Human Development Index (HDI) is a composite statistic of life expectancy, education, and income per capita indicators. <br />\n<br />\n睇下methodology啦呀港大仔<br />\n計分唔計思想觀念香港梗係高啦<br />\n香港人長命高學歷高收入可惜思想戇鳩"},{"pid":"1ab9b6a280af7752acb55bbf148652bcbcd2fd36","tid":120883,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:11:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cd2f917615f630f728d18f985be5fca899489e8","tid":120883,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>The Human Development Index (HDI) is a composite statistic of life expectancy, education, and income per capita indicators. <br />\n<br />\n睇下methodology啦呀港大仔<br />\n計分唔計思想觀念香港梗係高啦<br />\n香港人長命高學歷高收入可惜思想戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地依個計法計多好多年<br />\n唔通人地講巨無霸指數時你又話佢唔計豬柳蛋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港的確係依個數字高，依個係不爭嘅事實，而個數字代表到咩就第個話題啦"},{"pid":"4f65c1739046958a586332230c97bef6fe4aaeff","tid":120883,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本係亞洲第一 點會低過香港</blockquote><br />\n亞洲第一係新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇影響力"},{"pid":"c1f0782e9d3e50de6b3e59a0ec9b001bf8d16bde","tid":120883,"uid":49263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:18:18.000Z","msg":"點解港人咁拎長命？<br />\n香港度度都咁L污糟，生活又咁L大壓力<br />\n點解咁矛盾？"},{"pid":"295ab78e76a3bb8456191aadd0326c781a43c64b","tid":120883,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:22:32.000Z","msg":"又打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68eca6a3018c2988e503ff2e37f240973f59ba87","tid":120883,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解港人咁拎長命？<br />\n香港度度都咁L污糟，生活又咁L大壓力<br />\n點解咁矛盾？</blockquote><br />\n其實同其他發達國家只係爭少少，正常冇咩嚴重污染、交通安全、醫療好少少都做到"},{"pid":"bfd42ca3c6b6ece8e919428f86fa16345912196f","tid":120883,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講事實就打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講返樓價最高又唔見你話打j自抽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfdb0f78455cd624f45ca0ca07863a364f520e7","tid":120883,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:28:42.000Z","msg":"為人類（遊客）建樂園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffb0f023045032c4aec6e461321cc07a811dfb1","tid":120883,"uid":27960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講事實就打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講返樓價最高又唔見你話打j自抽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲傻仔自己差 又覺得全香港都陪佢一齊差<br />\n唔識欣賞自己地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927cd16281b9527bbcf6146c30a08736fb2140a9","tid":120883,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T19:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講事實就打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講返樓價最高又唔見你話打j自抽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲傻仔自己差 又覺得全香港都陪佢一齊差<br />\n唔識欣賞自己地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗欣賞<br />\n起碼對數字唔好咁偏見先<br />\n講香港樓價高、英文差過台灣差過越南就好興奮衝出話人港豬，話人唔接受事實<br />\n講人類發達指數、無知指數就出嚟話人打j，話假、唔持平<br />\n根本就唔抵得香港唔係全世界最差嘅地方，滿足唔到自己踩港嘅快感"},{"pid":"ae9949c9605bc46c9b55c0fb2203a6b8a272dd43","tid":120883,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T20:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解港人咁拎長命？<br />\n香港度度都咁L污糟，生活又咁L大壓力<br />\n點解咁矛盾？</blockquote><br />\n好多地方既人均壽命會俾嬰兒死亡率拖低。"},{"pid":"ed14f42acb612b4d52ce6681d2e2672e063a902c","tid":120883,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T20:32:10.000Z","msg":"新加坡0.912<br />\n果然越高分越低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f734a525269d823489cd0b0be8e311a111ab1e0c","tid":120883,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T23:55:26.000Z","msg":"香港成日贏係數字到"},{"pid":"c59c2fad7871f376d4cef4ca096175a9c2b47ff8","tid":120883,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:01:24.000Z","msg":"數字遊戲而己，有意義嗎？"},{"pid":"1f6f0c6e6ff356324a1aa16818621e327d0932b9","tid":120883,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數字遊戲而己，有意義嗎？</blockquote><br />\n冇特別意思，但總有人會話人講個數字出嚟係打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定有啲範疇係優勢先會高㗎啦，搵嚟講"},{"pid":"a15cce0d29c528d5b8a575f63c8e4d556fb39dbd","tid":120883,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:06:10.000Z","msg":"香港都唔係國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98644f3e3bd09203e1668868c0045a3ee96d83a9","tid":120883,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:09:58.000Z","msg":"應該咁講，香港的人係好極端，可以發展的年輕人發展潛力係好高的，相反，那些熱愛中國土匪廢佬就點極都唔明的！"},{"pid":"bb02ffafc3cc6d152a6bb01112c3559a3374ce57","tid":120883,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該咁講，香港的人係好極端，可以發展的年輕人發展潛力係好高的，相反，那些熱愛中國土匪廢佬就點極都唔明的！</blockquote><br />\n本身香港就係優秀人才俾垃圾政府管，而且垃圾政府政府為鞏固政權去資助去坐大冇腦嘅垃圾，而亦有一批人係為咗抽油水去話對抗政府，其實都係愚化香港人。<br />\n成件事本身就係因為香港係個反智嘅地方，孕育優秀人才嘅優秀政府冇辦法承接去另一個優秀嘅政府。"}]}